snippet.title: The Legend of Spyro: Dawn of the Dragon Mobile (J2ME mid-tier version) 100% speedrun in 9:56
snippet.description:
KEmulator 0.9.7, Java 8u351.

I definitely had better runs going, but they all died to the stupid jump in the volcano. This is not great but I think (unless there's gonna be competition) I'll do more runs when my new j2me phone arrives, since my current one has the TV-out issue.
